Came here for a quick bite a drinks, Bestia had board games which is a plus but it's too dark to play in there. Not sure if it was because we got there after 6 pm. I ordered sliders which were partially burnt and after we had enough of this place, (which took an hour) we had asked for the check. This is where a 3 star rating dropped to a 1, I wish I could give 0 stars because that is truly what this establishment deserves. It took the waitress (An older Spanish woman) 30 minutes to get us the check. It was about $45 and we gave her $60, then we waited for our change. 45 minutes pass and she finally shows up with our change and was upset by my demeanor once I got my change. Clearly I'd be upset after wasting over an entire hour just to pay for subpar service. She proceeded to argue with me, to the point where my party and I felt uncomfortable and left. Terrible food, and even worse customer service. I would not come back here nor recommend this place to anyone.
